ntextualise content for Kenyan markets \u2013 citing KNBS data, CBK regulations, or industry-specific reports. This prevents the generic \u201ccopy-paste\u201d problem common with low-cost outsourced content.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1388\" data-end=\"1432\">Q4: What if I need content in Swahili?<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1433\" data-end=\"1718\">We provide bilingual content in English and Kiswahili. For instance, NGOs running community campaigns often require Swahili leaflets, while corporates may prefer English-only reports. We adapt tone and vocabulary to suit the target audience, ensuring accuracy and cultural relevance.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1720\" data-end=\"1787\">Q5: Do you provide graphics and publishing too, or just text?<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1788\" data-end=\"1881\">Our core service is text, but we frequently integrate with design and publishing workflows:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1882\" data-end=\"2231\">\n<li data-start=\"1882\" data-end=\"1953\">\n<p data-start=\"1884\" data-end=\"1953\">Supplying content with layout suggestions for reports and brochures<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1954\" data-end=\"2015\">\n<p data-start=\"1956\" data-end=\"2015\">Preparing blog articles formatted for WordPress or Joomla<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2016\" data-end=\"2231\">\n<p data-start=\"2018\" data-end=\"2231\">Coordinating with your in-house or outsourced design teams<br data-start=\"2076\" data-end=\"2079\" \/>Where needed, we can package content with <strong data-start=\"2121\" data-end=\"2184\">basic graphics (infographics, charts, social media visuals)<\/strong> in collaboration with our creative partners.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row full_width=&#8221;stretch_row&#8221; bg_type=&#8221;bg_color&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1717845133697{padding-top: 30px !important;padding-bottom: 30px !important;}&#8221; bg_color_value=&#8221;#f4f4f4&#8243; el_id=&#8221;!\/contact&#8221;][vc_column]<div id=\"ultimate-heading-479